item.title: CVE-2023-2606|2024-08-02T06:26:09.823Z -- unknown -- wp%20brutal%20ai
item.description: The WP Brutal AI WordPress plugin before 2.06 does not sanitise and escape some of its settings, which could allow high privilege users such as admin to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed (for example in multisite setup).
